'''Yamashina Clan''' (山科家) was a {{ill|Japanese court noble|ja|公家|1=Kuge|12=draft|12=draft}} and later a {{ill|Kazoku|ja|華族|12=draft|12=draft}} family. As a {{ill|Kuge|ja|公家|1=Kuge|12=draft|12=draft}}, its Rank was {{ill|Baronial House|ja|羽林家|12=draft|12=draft}}, and as a {{ill|Kazoku|ja|華族|12=draft|12=draft}}, its title was that of a {{ill|Count|ja|伯爵|12=draft|12=draft}}.{{sfn|Odabe, Yūji|2006|p=326}}

